Mazda Plastic Model Kits
Welcome to the most comprehensive Mazda plastic model kit (Scale Models) list on the net. At the Moment this page is far from complete, I am always adding new models to this page. Please click on the thumb nail size picture to see a larger and more pictures in addition to these pictures you will see a review of each kit (at this stage it is only the kits that I own that have the reviews). Any kits with the  sign beside it I am looking for, so if you have any of these kits for sale please give me an email ask_us@drmaz.com  you can also email me at the same address if you have some thing you would like to this list.

This list may take anywhere from a few seconds to a minute to show (download) upon your screen depending on your internet connection speed. Please be patient it is worth the wait.
